<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <meta name="description" content="LAB 3: File Upload – Bypass Validasi Ekstensi Gambar" />
  <title><%= title %> | CyberLAB</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;600&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>

<%- include('partials/navbar') %>

<main class="main-content">

  <!-- PAGE HEADER -->
  <div class="page-header vuln-page-header">
    <div class="page-header-inner">
      <div class="lab-badge vuln-badge">⚠️ VULNERABLE LEVEL 3</div>
      <h1>📁 LAB 3: Bypass Validasi Ekstensi Gambar</h1>
      <p>Simulasi validasi yang mengharuskan ekstensi gambar saja, namun **tanpa validasi MIME type yang sesungguhnya**.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- NAVIGATION SUB-LABS -->
  <div style="display:flex; gap:0.5rem; margin-bottom:2rem; flex-wrap:wrap;">
    <a href="/lab/file-upload/1" class="btn btn-outline">Level 1: No Validation</a>
    <a href="/lab/file-upload/2" class="btn btn-outline">Level 2: Blacklist Filter</a>
    <a href="/lab/file-upload/3" class="btn btn-vuln" style="border: 2px solid var(--accent-red)">Level 3: Extension Whitelist</a>
    <a href="/lab/file-upload/fixed" class="btn btn-fixed">Level 4: Secure Version</a>
  </div>

  <div class="lab-container">

    <!-- KONSEP -->
    <section class="lab-section">
      <h2>📖 Konsep MIME Type &amp; Client-Side Validation</h2>
      <div class="concept-box">
        <p>Banyak developer membatasi jenis file menggunakan filter ekstensi whitelist (misal: hanya menerima <code>.jpg</code>, <code>.png</code>). Namun, jika pemeriksaan tersebut hanya mengandalkan pengecekan tipe MIME / Content-Type yang dikirimkan oleh browser client, validasi tersebut sangat mudah dimanipulasi.</p>
        <p>Dengan menggunakan alat proxy seperti **Burp Suite**, penyerang dapat mengubah isi payload, merubah ekstensi nama file, namun memalsukan header <code>Content-Type: image/jpeg</code> agar disetujui server.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FORM UPLOAD -->
    <section class="lab-section">
      <h2>🧪 Latihan Bypass dengan Burp Suite</h2>
      <div class="vuln-box">
        <div class="vuln-label">⚠️ Endpoint: <code>POST /lab/file-upload/3/upload</code></div>

        <% if (message) { %>
          <div class="alert alert-success"><%= message %></div>
        <% } %>
        <% if (error) { %>
          <div class="alert alert-error"><%= error %></div>
        <% } %>

        <form action="/lab/file-upload/3/upload" method="POST" enctype="multipart/form-data" class="upload-form">
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="file-input">Pilih file untuk diupload:</label>
            <div class="file-input-wrapper">
              <input type="file" name="file" id="file-input" class="file-input" accept=".jpg,.jpeg,.png" />
              <div class="file-input-display" id="file-display">Belum ada file dipilih...</div>
            </div>
            <small class="form-hint text-red">⚠️ Whitelist aktif: Server hanya mengizinkan nama file berakhiran <code>.jpg</code>, <code>.jpeg</code>, atau <code>.png</code>.</small>
          </div>
          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-vuln-submit" id="btn-upload-vuln">📤 Upload File (Level 3)</button>
        </form>

        <!-- TIPS CHALLENGE -->
        <div class="webshell-demo" style="border-color:var(--accent-orange); background:rgba(255,123,53,0.03);">
          <h4 style="color:var(--accent-orange)">🦊 Panduan Bypass MIME / Content-Type dengan Burp Suite:</h4>
          <div class="steps-list" style="margin-top:0.5rem;">
            <div class="step-item">
              <span class="step-num">1</span>
              <div>
                <strong>Persiapan Berkas:</strong>
                <p>Siapkan webshell Anda dengan nama berekstensi gambar, misalnya <code>evil.jpg</code> (isi file tetap merupakan kode php/html webshell Anda).</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="step-item">
              <span class="step-num">2</span>
              <div>
                <strong>Intercept Upload Request:</strong>
                <p>Aktifkan Burp Suite Intercept ON, lalu klik unggah file <code>evil.jpg</code>.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="step-item">
              <span class="step-num">3</span>
              <div>
                <strong>Ubah Ekstensi di dalam Burp:</strong>
                <p>Di jendela intercept Burp Suite, temukan parameter <code>filename="evil.jpg"</code> dan ubah menjadi <code>filename="evil.php"</code>. Pastikan header <code>Content-Type: image/jpeg</code> di bawahnya tetap dipertahankan agar lolos filter content-type. Klik Forward!</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- LIST FILE -->
    <% if (files && files.length > 0) { %>
    <section class="lab-section">
      <h2>📂 Daftar File yang Diunggah</h2>
      <div class="vuln-box">
        <table class="file-table">
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th>Nama File</th>
              <th>Ukuran</th>
              <th>Aksi / URL</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <% files.forEach(function(f) { %>
            <tr>
              <td><code><%= f.name %></code></td>
              <td><%= (f.size / 1024).toFixed(2) %> KB</td>
              <td><a href="<%= f.url %>" target="_blank" class="file-link"><%= f.url %></a></td>
            </tr>
            <% }); %>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </section>
    <% } %>

  </div>
</main>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>

<script>
  document.getElementById('file-input').addEventListener('change', function() {
    const display = document.getElementById('file-display');
    display.textContent = this.files[0] ? this.files[0].name + ' (' + (this.files[0].size / 1024).toFixed(2) + ' KB)' : 'Belum ada file dipilih...';
  });
</script>
</body>
</html>
